data.description: This beautiful waterfront home is looking for its new owner. At over 2500 square feet and sitting on 2.37 cleared acres, this home offers the space and tranquility that any family would love. Beautiful mature oaks and fruit trees are scattered throughout the property, and the huge deck that is accessible from the formal dining area allows views of the beautiful bayou and gorgeous southern sunsets. The downstairs workshop area also has a half bath for added convenience.  With a little TLC, this home could be everything you've been looking for! Schedule your appointment to view today!
